Class TupleXYZ

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.gsfc.spdf.ssc.TupleXYZ

public class TupleXYZ
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a 3-element tuple that is represented by double-precision floating point x,y,z coordinates.
